description:
Minecraft modded. Iskall and myself decided to team up together to take on Enigmatica 2 Expert mode. The plan is to try build a base together while we each focus on different areas of the modpack. 

We will probably record together occasionally, but most of the series will be from our solo perspectives... so make sure to check out Iskall's side of the adventure as well.
